snippet.title: Broken Lens - Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover the trailer of our upcoming game Broken Lens

✨With Broken Lens, renew the experience of a classic game of your childhood by spotting the differences between two scenes in a cute and cosy universe 🔍

Demo available and don't forget to wishlist 🧡

🎬 Minoe & Hatebreed
🎹 Yomoeh
🎨 EncreMecanique
